Minties moment
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an embarrassing (often comical) mistake in a sporting situation etc. (as shown in Minties television ads)
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: alluding to the slogan (for Minties the mint-flavoured sweets), 'It's moments like these you need Minties'
